  "titles": "Mortarion Primarch of the Death Guard, The Pale King, the Traveller, Dread Liberator of Barbaras",
  "lore": "The shadowed and sinister Mortarion was Primarch and commander of the Death Guard Legion. Raised upon a nightmare world of fell secrets and horror where humans were hunted like animals, a darkness surrounded him and would never leave him. Fiercely driven and relentless, the reaper-Primarch led his Legion to become wrathful liberators, spectres of death and judgement to whom no battlefield was insurmountable and no foe too terrible to face. With lies and half-truths did Horus sway Mortarion to his cause, and the price that he and his Legion would pay for their role in the Horus Heresy would be nightmarish beyond imagining.",
